OL,3,CNewcastle footfall down by roughly
OL,4,Cfifth due to fears of riots
OL,6,FKris Jepson reports on the businesses
OL,7,Fimpacted by fears over two protests
OL,8,Fthat took place over the weekend,
OL,9,Fwhich ended peacefully.
OL,11,FNewcastle city centre footfall was
OL,12,Fdown by an estimated 20 per cent last
OL,13,Fdue to fears over potential rioting.
OL,15,FThe concern was sparked by a series of
OL,16,Friots across the country, influenced
OL,17,Fby elements of the Far Right online
OL,18,Fover the past fortnight, following the
OL,19,Fdeaths of three children in Southport.
