OL,3,CNewcastle footfall down by roughly
OL,4,Cfifth due to fears of riots
OL,6,FIn the North East, riots broke out in
OL,7,FHartlepool, Sunderland and
OL,8,FMiddlesbrough, leaving business owners
OL,9,Fand residents in Newcastle fearful of
OL,10,Fwhat might happen on Saturday, where
OL,11,Ftwo protests were planned.
OL,13,FThe anti-immigration protest took
OL,14,Fplace on Saturday morning at the Bigg
OL,15,FMarket, and no more than 100 peaceful
OL,16,Fprotesters took part.
