OL,4,Cfifth due to fears of riots
OL,6,FThe protesters listened to speeches
OL,7,Fand chanted anti-hate slogans, and
OL,8,Fsaid they were there to protest
OL,9,Fagainst the violence and disorder that
OL,10,Fhad occurred.
OL,12,FThe business group NE1 said it was
OL,13,Fwelcome relief that peaceful protests
OL,14,Fdid not end in disorder over the
OL,15,Fweekend, but said they had caused a 20
OL,16,Fper cent decline in footfall for much
OL,17,Fof last week in the city.
