OL,3,CNewcastle footfall down by roughly
OL,4,Cfifth due to fears of riots
OL,6,FStephen Patterson from NE1 told ITV
OL,7,FNews: "Obviously people were hearing
OL,8,Fthings. There were concerns and they
OL,9,Fwere cancelling bookings, you know,
OL,10,Frestaurants were previously fully
OL,11,Fbooked, then cancelling bookings as a
OL,12,Fresult. So we estimate at this point
OL,13,Fin time that we're probably down
OL,14,Faround 20 per cent in terms of the
OL,15,Fcity's footfall from Wednesday
OL,16,Fonwards."
