OL,6,FHe added: "It is our civic space, our
OL,7,Fpublic realm. Those are the areas our
OL,8,Fcommunity really comes together and
OL,9,Fwe've seen that a lot over the start
OL,10,Fof the summer, with the activity in
OL,11,FOld Eldon Square, down on the
OL,12,FQuayside, families coming out and
OL,13,Fenjoying the city. That's what we want
OL,14,Fto see.
