OL,6,F"It's difficult as well. We had
OL,7,FRestaurant Week last week, and it is
OL,8,Fonly a week, but we are absolutely
OL,9,Fextending it for another week to
OL,10,Fprovide that opportunity for people
OL,11,Fwho couldn't take advantage of it last
OL,12,Fweek."
OL,14,FA handful of businesses boarded up
OL,15,Ftheir windows ahead of the protests,
OL,16,Fbut one, the Chilli Flame restaurant
OL,17,Fand takeaway on Newgate Street,
OL,18,Fdecided against it after talking to
OL,19,Fthe police.
