OL,6,FMuhammad Farooq Khan from Chilli Flame
OL,7,Ftold ITV News: "We took all the
OL,8,Fprecautions to take care of our shop,
OL,9,Fbecause there's windows all around. We
OL,10,Fdidn't cover it, but I was very
OL,11,Fworried about my shop and the business
OL,12,Fbasically, so when police came in,
OL,13,Fthey gave us the confidence that
OL,14,Fnothing would happen, and on the
OL,15,FSaturday, when it happened, we were
OL,16,Freally secure and satisfied."
