OL,6,FBlackfriars Restaurant had safety
OL,7,Fconcerns over its staff and customers
OL,8,Fand said there was still had an
OL,9,Feconomic impact on the business
OL,10,Fdespite protests ending peacefully.
OL,12,FTalking to ITV News, Andy Hull from
OL,13,FBlackfriars said: "Safety of our staff
OL,14,Fis the most important thing, and that
OL,15,Fof our customers and we just wanted to
OL,16,Fmake sure that everyone was safe and
OL,17,Fthey were happy to come in and then we
OL,18,Fhad to take the financial hit on the
OL,19,Fchin.
